⚙️ @aidungeon by Latitude runs large-scale mixture-of-experts models at a fraction of the cost — $0.05 per million tokens, down from $0.20.

@DeepInfra inference platform makes this possible, powered by NVIDIA Blackwell GPUs, NVFP4, and TensorRT LLM.

🔗 Read the blog: https://t.co/MyvmT1eWsd

// From Vibe Coding to Agentic Engineering //

GLM-5 is a foundation model designed to transition from vibe coding to agentic engineering.

The model introduces novel asynchronous agent RL algorithms that enable learning from complex, long-horizon interactions. It also adopts DSA https://t.co/ZjJhJmDLPQ
